## Notes
- URL: https://github.com/PriorLabs/TabPFN
- Nature Article: https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-024-08328-6
- TabPFN is a Foundation Model for Tabular Data.
- Key feature: Zero hyperparameter tuning and no training time (it's a Prior-data Fitted Network).
- Performance: Outperforms XGBoost, LightGBM, CatBoost on datasets up to 10k-50k samples.
- Business Use Case: Predicting sales, customer churn, or trends from CSV/Excel data without needing a data scientist to tune models.

